==English==
===Pronunciation===
*mīnd, /maɪnd/, /<tt>maInd</tt>/
*:'''Homophones''': [[mine]]d
*:[[Rhymes:English:-aɪnd|Rhymes: -aɪnd]]

===Noun===
'''mind''' ([[minds]])

#The capacity for [[rational]] [[thought]]; the supposed site of such rational thought; the [[psyche]].
#The [[brain]].
#A caring for the problem. ''A mind to the madness.''

